# <type>(<scope>): <subject>   ← ≤72 chars, imperative ("add", not "added")
#
# <body>  ← WHY, not what. Required when the diff is >50 LOC. Wrap at 72.
#
# <trailers>
#   Closes #123
#   Co-Authored-By: Name <email>
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <what broke and the migration>
#   Tag: v1.2.3        ← optional strict-SemVer release tag (see apply_tag_trailer.py)
#
# ── types ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   feat | fix | refactor | perf | docs | test | build | ci | chore | revert
#   (type must match what the diff actually does)
#
# ── scopes (EDIT THESE for your project) ────────────────────────────────
#   core | cli | api | ui | docs | build | ci | deps | meta
#
# Install once:  git config commit.template .gitmessage
